In the midst of the new political formations, is Wiper leader Kalonzo Musyoka the most “beautiful girl in the room” so to speak, for deputy president DR. William Ruto? Well, it appears Ruto’s quest to succeed president Uhuru Kenyatta now seeks to rope in the former vice president. Ibrahim karanja reports on how a funeral for mama Rael Mbellete Mailu mother to former CS Cleopa Mailu, turned into an avenue to woo Kalonzo to say yes to Ruto.